-12-27T08:33:31.000Z","msg":"有北美唔揀揀大陸<br />\n唔係on9係咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T08:48:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#76776 - 一鋪過</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請大家保持批判性思考，善用不推文回覆，該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>感動既係LOL World Championship 又係中国人贏！！我係中国人呀ｈｉ:~( - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/30/162455_b95b23fb4ab68670a4733f7d69d7a701.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F162455_b95b23fb4ab68670a4733f7d69d7a701.png&h=912f7af4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1703944/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1703944/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>今日香港人是咪好嬲？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？ - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>聽朝準時返工表達不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1690782/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1690782/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>宜家班勇武示威者癲到玩埋土製炸彈, 同工聯會暴徒有乜分別? 今次一次要割了 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/nVWEx2b.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1651704/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1651704/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>林鄭媽媽果然有計, 蒙面法一實施俾你班友玩幾日, 到今個星期加埋黨鐵宵禁, 呢個星期終於靜左 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>林鄭媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n,希望可以繼續落去還我正常生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1643169/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1643169/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>黃之鋒再次賣港- 德國演說 &quot; Hong Kong is Part of China &quot; - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/11/xelVBc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F11%2FxelVBc.png&h=c48ea686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地做咁多野都係晒鳩氣<br />\n一鋪俾佢搞灣<br />\n中共都屈你港獨之首啦, 咁你咪認撚左佢lor. 扮乜野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通你講句Hong Kong is Part of China就會俾你再返大陸咩<br />\n<br />\n睇下我地呢3個月不斷講Hong Kong is not china<br />\n晒鳩氣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/sports/page/800/2015/11/18/54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fsports%2Fpage%2F800%2F2015%2F11%2F18%2F54.jpg&h=b9eb8cb9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1559448/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1559448/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f760ff07b7695a3ebbd1aff8508ff6e81823b121","tid":1799233,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:13:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ba303ba7205bad448c5979002b75949b2b40b85d","tid":1799233,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:17:18.000Z","msg":"主動啲<br />\n改變消費模式"},{"pid":"e