段時期的長度有所不同，但一般是指1986年12月到1991年2月之間共4年3個月的時期。這是日本戰後僅次於1960年代後期的經濟高速發展的第二次大發展時期。<br />\n這次經濟浪潮受到了大量投機活動的支撐，因此隨着1990年代初泡沫破裂，日本經濟出現大倒退，此後進入了平成大蕭條時期。<br />\n日語中「平成景氣」基本與此同義，但有時也包括此後的經濟蕭條階段。"},{"pid":"0dbb50b855bcbb795a16a5738a3737f725a2e877","tid":1799233,"uid":309268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T09:18:45.000Z","msg":"支爆近了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 唯一出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4432d4a84f34a65ca2fad9f28626f578d2727a16","tid":1799233,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dbb50b855bcbb795a16a5738a3737f725a2e877","tid":1799233,"uid":309268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T09:18:45.000Z","msg":"支爆近了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 唯一出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T09:22:39.000Z","msg":"似乎就快"},{"pid":"d69a3f39a9291327568d5b6f1e5da76751192b61","tid":1799233,"uid":18772,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T09:33:54.000Z","msg":"希臘咁大既地方2000億就叫苦連天<br />\n大陸冇咩生產力既地方一冇生意少少錢唔緊要<br />\n但係咁多地方加埋一定無能力應付<br />\n生意大陸本身都搞到差晒  係時候用身體償還"},{"pid":"250d38d07bffcdbe0ab532058740808c72f8ff0e","tid":1799233,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T09:35:10.000Z","msg":"無限數冚數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed996be9779c59360e5776470c43fc88fdf52c84","tid":1799233,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"250d38d07bffcdbe0ab532058740808c72f8ff0e","tid":1799233,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T09:35:10.000Z","msg":"無限數冚數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T09:35:48.000Z","msg":"印錢<br />\nCNY M2&gt; USD M2+EURO M2....."},{"pid":"fda6883b790c5f0598bf117df175d351